    <text>
        <body>
            <head>35. Memorandum From the President’s Assistant for National Security Affairs
                    (<persName corresp="rec5nWAotd8wedNxI">Clark</persName>) to President <persName
                    corresp="rec5PPNCl6qqfgBAq">Reagan</persName><note n="1" place="foot"
                    type="source" xml:id="d35fn1">Source: National Security Council, <orgName
                        corresp="recft7WGb7Fww0wma">National Security Council</orgName>
                    Institutional Files, Box SR 079, <gloss target="#t_NSDD_1">NSDD</gloss> 053
                        [<gloss target="#t_START_1"><rs corresp="recGzN4S83GSdMO7O" type="event"
                            >START</rs></gloss> IV]. Secret. Sent for action. Prepared by <persName
                        corresp="rec3WaAgwEDeqcFLV">Linhard</persName> and <persName
                        corresp="rec1MI7pNjlwnDZyR">Kraemer</persName>. A stamped notation indicates
                        <persName corresp="rec5PPNCl6qqfgBAq">Reagan</persName> saw the
                    memorandum.</note>
            </head>
            <opener>
                <dateline rendition="#right">
                    <placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1982-08-30"
                        >August 30, 1982</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <list type="subject">
                <head>SUBJECT</head>
                <item>Draft <gloss target="#t_NSDD_1">NSDD</gloss> Reflecting Decisions Reached at
                    August 9 <gloss target="#t_NSC_1"><orgName corresp="recft7WGb7Fww0wma"
                            >NSC</orgName></gloss> Meeting</item>
            </list>
            <p rendition="#sectiontitleital">Issue</p>
            <p>Should you approve/sign the attached <gloss target="#t_NSDD_1">NSDD</gloss>?<note
                    n="2" place="foot" xml:id="d35fn2">See <ref target="#d36">Document
                    36</ref>.</note>
            </p>
            <p rendition="#sectiontitleital">Facts</p>
            <p>The attached draft <gloss target="#t_NSDD_1">NSDD</gloss> (Tab A) does the
                following:</p>
            <p>—reflects the decisions reached at the August 9th <gloss target="#t_NSC_1"><orgName
                        corresp="recft7WGb7Fww0wma">NSC</orgName></gloss> meeting on <gloss
                    target="#t_START_1"><rs corresp="recGzN4S83GSdMO7O" type="event"
                    >START</rs></gloss>;<note n="3" place="foot" xml:id="d35fn3">See <ref
                        target="#d32">Document 32</ref>.</note>
            </p>
            <p>—provides guidance on <rs corresp="recvMEtDFpnXkyj45" type="topic">verification</rs>
                measures associated with those decisions (with the guidance drawn from the
                Interdepartmental Paper developed to support the <gloss target="#t_NSC_1"><orgName
                        corresp="recft7WGb7Fww0wma">NSC</orgName></gloss> meeting); and</p>
            <p>—tasks additional Interdepartmental work.</p>
            <pb facs="0140" n="111" xml:id="pg_111"/>
            <p rendition="#sectiontitleital">Discussion</p>
            <p>We have discussed this draft <gloss target="#t_NSDD_1">NSDD</gloss> with <orgName
                    corresp="rec7Bg5QUDG0eHqgl">State</orgName> and <orgName
                    corresp="recjQ97iMHKp6vwlA">Defense</orgName>, and we feel it is ready for your
                approval and signature.</p>
            <p rendition="#sectiontitleital">Recommendation</p>
            <table cols="3">
                <row>
                    <cell>
                        <hi rendition="simple_italic">OK</hi>
                    </cell>
                    <cell>
                        <hi rendition="simple_italic">NO</hi>
                    </cell>
                    <cell/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>________</cell>
                    <cell>________</cell>
                    <cell>That you approve and sign the draft <gloss target="#t_NSDD_1">NSDD</gloss>
                        provided at Tab A.<note n="4" place="foot" xml:id="d35fn4"><persName
                                corresp="rec5PPNCl6qqfgBAq">Reagan</persName> initialed his
                            approval.</note>
                    </cell>
                </row>
            </table>
        </body>
    </text>
